short_description:
Here are some my snippets which are developing independently for using in some current and future projects:
- simple realisation of binary search trees;
- realisation of bidirectional list and simple queues;
- morphological operations with images (erosion, dilation, connected components search);
- wavefront decomposition by Zernike polynomials & reconstruction of Zernike by gradient field to wavefront;
- simple CLI interface for motorized linear translator Standa 8MT175-150 moving by SMSD-1.5 driver.
